CCR2D1Picture
=============
A format to encode pictures for use in CCR2D1.

Header
------
{'C', 'C', 'R', '2', 'D', '1', 'P', '\x01'}

Properties
----------
{width << 24, width << 16, width <<  8, width,
height << 24, height<< 16, height<<  8, height}

Pixels
------
for each pixel
	{color.length, color, dnsty.length, dnsty}


CCR2D1CompressedPicture
=======================
CCR2D1Ps might be compressed with GZip in the future, but it's too
much of a hassle right now.
